'''Hershoon the Destroyer''' was a being existing in [[Mizx]] mythology. He was a being of immense evil. According to legend, he was able to live on beyond his death by invoking strong magics while on his deathbed and placing pieces of his soul into the bodies of the [[ibliton]].<ref name="CotG">''[[Creatures of the Galaxy]]''</ref>

